Type: Package
Package: gwasim
Title: Simulates phenotypes with given effects based on provided
    data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marcin Kierczak
Maintainer: The package maintainer <marcin.kierczak@scilifelab.se>
Description: Package contains functions for simulating
    phenotypes using provided genotyping data, with desired effect sizes
    and directionalities. Mainly used for benchmarking different GWAS
    methods.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    tidyverse,
    magrittr,
    seqminer
Imports:
    SKAT,
    lifecycle
Suggests: 
    GenABEL,
    vcfR,
    covr,
    testthat,
    devtools
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
RdMacros: lifecycle
